41,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"有係人12月生日係無咩人錫同成日比人蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為你係全班最細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係朋友身邊只有附和佢地，你比意見就ban <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為做最大可以牽住班朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做細只可以聽"},{"pid":"5ab1ae399a3b90f0547ad37307b9ed2db2a073f7","tid":20961,"uid":52983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"12月撞正冬至生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事好warm"},{"pid":"b94c5b066efd9ab2d5393c1c1db1063cac213a6c","tid":20961,"uid":8719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"11月尾生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人錫 成績都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算同年果啲未到年尾我都細佢一歲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3c474f90122c511a3532543cf0b4901a575b67","tid":20961,"uid":49874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e697d2a56e797ee05f6620ab8620323c6787f897","tid":20961,"uid":49874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55761251d1b45d9da0bfe655d8b541b0c95100a9","tid":20961,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:14:49.000Z","msg":"年尾都好型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6220f6922416e4d22c3cf0868155fc53f2431216","tid":20961,"uid":4293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"生日撞正exam period<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38313f70a2e4559e8d5c5aa3d6bf3e3